This template is for use on an article's ''talk'' page to show that the article's infobox needs to be converted.  As well as adding the message to the talk page, it adds the page to an appropriate category for cleanup.

==Usage==
This template <em>goes on an article's talk page</em>, not on the article itself because infobox formatting or replacement is not an article content issue, unless the old/broken infobox raises a verifiability, POV or content dispute issue. Use one of the types below as a '''type''' parameter, for example: <code><nowiki>{{newinfobox|type=single}}</nowiki></code>.

